Package: rusbmux
Version: VERSION_PLACEHOLDER
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: ARCH_PLACEHOLDER
Maintainer: Abdullah Al-Banna <abdu.albanna@proton.me>
Depends: libc6, libgcc-s1
Recommends: systemd
Provides: rusbmux, usbmuxd
Conflicts: usbmuxd
Replaces: usbmuxd
Description: A usbmuxd replacement in pure Rust
 rusbmux is a drop-in replacement for usbmuxd, written in pure Rust.
 It provides USB multiplexing for Apple devices, supporting both
 USB and WiFi connections. It works with libimobiledevice, idevice,
 3uTools, iTunes, and other tools that use usbmuxd.
Homepage: https://github.com/abdullah-albanna/rusbmux
